name: Louis Vuitton Print T-Shirt
shortDescription: This playful T-shirt combines a Louis Vuitton signature with a cool, laid-back vibe. Crafted from soft cotton jersey, it is printed on the inside with a Louis Vuitton motif, creating a reversed and slightly faded effect when worn. A palladium chain detail adds an iconic finishing touch.
detailedDescription:
• 100% cotton
  • White
  • Regular fit
  • Model wears size S
  • Model measurements: bust 81 cm/24 inches, height 178 cm/5 foot 10 inches, waist 61 cm/24 inches, hips 88 cm/34 inches
  • Made in Italy

name: Louis Vuitton Print T-Shirt
shortDescription: This playful piece twists a basic T-shirt shape with a reversed Louis Vuitton signature. The motif is printed on the cotton jersey fabric with a distinctive mottled effect. The House’s iconic chain detail adds a finishing touch to the piece.

  • Black
  • Regular fit
  • Model wears size S

name: Side Strap T-Shirt
shortDescription: Crafted from soft jersey, the Side Strap T-Shirt offers a contemporary spin on the classic wardrobe staple. It features an adjustable waist, which is evocative of kimono obi belts thanks to its fabric side straps and iconic metallic D-ring. Gold-tone Monogram Flower details embellish the neckline.

name: Frill Blouse
shortDescription: With subtle ruffle accents on the sleeves and collar, this Frill Blouse is an enchanting piece. Gold-tone details catch the light in the form of Monogram Flowers on the front and LV buttons at the neck. The blouse has been made from soft cotton poplin and features Monogram fil coupé to create an elegant piece.

  • Optic White
  • Slightly boxy
  • Made in Italy
  • Do not wash
  • Do not bleach
  • Do not tumble dry

name: Monogram Pocket T-Shirt
shortDescription: This T-shirt is a Louis Vuitton essential in a slightly tapered fit cut from soft, comfortable cotton jersey. The patch pocket is elegantly signed with Monogram silk trimmed with a graphic stripe accent, reminiscent of the borders of classic silk scarves. An LV chain detail adds a contemporary House touch to the neckline.

name: Rhinestone Mahina T-Shirt
shortDescription: A seasonal signature elevates a timeless clothing staple. This T-shirt is playfully signed all over with the delicate Mahina Monogram motif in a sparkly rhinestone finish. It is cut from soft, comfortable cotton jersey in a classic straight-cut shape with a sporty ribbed crew neckline for versatile daily styling.

name: Stencil Signature T-Shirt
shortDescription: This classic T-shirt is playfully signed on the chest with a vintage-effect Louis Vuitton print that nods to the stencilled signatures on the House’s archival travel trunks. This casual clothing piece is crafted from cotton jersey in a timeless straight-cut shape with a crew neckline trimmed with a chic LV chain embellishment.

name: Studded LV Sweater
shortDescription: This staple sweater has a clean, contemporary feel in soft cotton-blend jersey. It is cut in a casual long-sleeved shape with ribbed hems for a timeless look, while the front is embellished with the iconic LV Initials picked out in a shiny, studded finish for a chic signature touch.
detailedDescription:
• Main material: 89% cotton, 11% polyamide
  • Shining Black
  • Made in Italy

name: Cape Sleeve Blouse
shortDescription: The front of this breezy silk blouse has an understated contemporary aesthetic in a clean-cut oversized shape with a simple rounded neckline. At the back, the billowing long sleeves connect to form a fluid cape-like layer, adding romantic volume to the boxy silhouette. Contrasting cufflinks complete the clothing look with a graphic touch.

name: Trompe L’Oeil Scarf Top
shortDescription: This trompe l’oeil top from the runway showcases the House’s savoir-faire with couture levels of craftsmanship. It is made from a soft, lustrous cashmere-silk blend in a subtle striped motif. The sophisticated cropped silhouette drapes across the front and falls gracefully over the shoulders for a scarf-like effect, complete with a zip fastening at the back.

name: Utility Strip Silk Shirt
shortDescription: A standout style from the runway, this shirt is crafted from lightweight, sheer silk gauze with a graphic array of horizontal and vertical strips across the shoulders and body for a structured utility feel. It is cut with a clean standing collar trimmed with three buttons and wrist-grazing sleeves that underscore the boxy shape.

name: Utility Strip Silk Shirt
shortDescription: A standout style from the runway, this shirt is crafted from lightweight, sheer silk gauze with a graphic array of horizontal and vertical strips across the shoulders and body for a structured utility feel. It is cut with a clean standing collar trimmed with three buttons and wrist-grazing sleeves that underscore the boxy shape.

name: Colour-Blocked Corset Top
shortDescription: This contemporary corset top combines clean lines with graphic colour-blocking for a striking statement look. It is crafted from thick, structured silk faille in a sharp silhouette that offsets a straight neckline with a dramatically curved hem, while alternating flashes of black and grey create a flattering effect. It fastens at the side with an LV zip.

name: Monogram Flower Mountain T-Shirt
shortDescription: This T-shirt nods to dynamic winter sports style with a large print of a mountain detailed with an oversized Monogram Flower motif, a chunky Louis Vuitton signature and graphic, colourful stripes. Cut from soft cotton jersey in a classic fit, the crew neckline is trimmed with a chic LV chain embellishment for a final House touch.

name: Winter Bloom Technical Top
shortDescription: This long-sleeved top from the ski capsule is cut from technical stretch jersey that skims and sculpts the figure for a sleek silhouette. It is printed all over with a romantic winter bloom motif, while the outer arms, standing collar and front zip are highlighted with contrasting accents for a sporty look, which is emphasised by thumb holes in the cuffs.

name: Jewel Button Knit Top
shortDescription: This elegant knit top is spun from a soft compact wool blend in a chic cropped shape with short sleeves. The neckline is highlighted with a shimmering beaded trim, while the LV Night Collection’s ornate oversized jewel buttons add an elevated modern touch to the back.
detailedDescription:
• Main material: 98% wool, 1% polyamide, 1% elastane
  • Red
  • Made in Italy

name: Monogram Accent Lavallière Blouse
shortDescription: Seasonal detailing elevates this blouse with a sophisticated modern spirit. Tailored from soft, fluid silk crepe de chine in a refined finish, pleating introduces gentle volume to the straight-cut silhouette. The lavallière collar is delicately signed with metallic Monogram Flower accents and can be removed, thanks to an exposed zip around the neckline.

name: Jewel Button Mikado Blouse
shortDescription: This blouse has a smart, structured look in crisp wool-silk mikado tailored in a boxy straight cut, which is emphasised with shoulder pads. The front has a subtle layered effect with the LV Night Collection’s signature jewel buttons adding a dressy detail to the shoulders and hips. It is fastened at the back with an exposed zip.

name: LV Circle Sequin Crop Top
shortDescription: Shimmering all-over sequin embroidery elevates this chic crop top into a celebratory seasonal statement from the LV Night Collection. Crafted on a base of lightweight stretch tulle, the chest is signed with a sparkling LV Circle motif in contrasting sequins, while an LV chain embellishment adds a final House touch to the neckline.

name: Broderie Anglaise Collar Shirt
shortDescription: This shirt is tailored from lightweight cotton voile in an elegant tone-on-tone striped finish. It is crafted in a breezy straight-cut shape with smart buttoned cuffs, while a dainty Peter Pan collar detailed with contrasting broderie anglaise completes the look with a romantic yet graphic twist.

name: LV Circle Sequin T-Shirt
shortDescription: This casual oversized T-shirt is elevated into a seasonal statement with dazzling all-over sequin embroidery, crafted on a base of lightweight stretch tulle for a fluid, glittering finish. An LV Circle signature is picked out in contrasting sequins on the chest, while the neckline is embellished with an LV chain detail for a final House touch.

name: Sequin Pyjama Shirt
shortDescription: This button-up pyjama shirt from the LV Night Collection makes a shimmering statement with glittering sequins embroidered onto a contrasting base of stretch tulle for a bold, fluid finish. The classic loungewear style is detailed with a chic notched collar, graphic piping and three patch pockets, one of which is signed with an LV Circle motif.
